{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.040", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.560", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.480", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe B\u00fcrger! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.680", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In dieser Woche diskutieren wir \u00fcber den Fahrplan der n\u00e4chsten Bundesregierung und wie Deutschland in der n\u00e4chsten Wahlperiode regiert werden soll. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.520", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Koalitionsvertrag ist ern\u00fcchternd und entt\u00e4uschend zugleich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.040", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nicht mehr als f\u00fcnf Seiten ist Ihnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.720", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren der Koalitionsparteien, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.240", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unsere Sozialpolitik wert\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.400", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "5 von 175\u00a0Seiten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.560", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei nimmt der Einzelplan \u201eArbeit und Soziales\u201c rund 42\u00a0Prozent des geplanten Bundeshaushalts f\u00fcr 2018 ein und ist damit der gr\u00f6\u00dfte Posten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.200", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit dem Koalitionsvertrag wollen Sie mehr Gerechtigkeit schaffen und produzieren im Bereich der M\u00fctterrente weitere Ungerechtigkeiten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.080", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn Ihnen wirklich daran gelegen w\u00e4re, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.840", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mehr Gerechtigkeit einzuf\u00fchren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.280", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann w\u00fcrden Sie die M\u00fctterrente\u00a0II nicht erst ab dem dritten Kind zahlen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.120", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern generell an alle M\u00fctter."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.480", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit w\u00fcrden Sie diese Ungleichbehandlung von M\u00fcttern reell aus der Welt schaffen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.440", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die M\u00fctterrente darf au\u00dferdem nicht aus Mitteln der Rentenversicherung finanziert werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.880", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da es sich hierbei um versicherungsfremde Leistungen handelt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.720", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Darauf werden wir achten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.040", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihre Ank\u00fcndigung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.000", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass eine Rentenkommission bis 2020 ein Konzept zur Rente vorlegen soll, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.800", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist jetzt auch kein gro\u00dfer Wurf."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.080", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie lange sind Sie in der Regierung? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.040", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie lange sind die Schwierigkeiten in der gesetzlichen Rentenversicherung schon bekannt? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.760", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Warum haben Sie nicht schon l\u00e4ngst ein eigenes Konzept vorgelegt?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.720", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein Konzept erstellen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.480", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "analysieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.520", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "evaluieren\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.920", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit dieser Strategie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.920", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.520", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "schieben Sie die Verantwortung der n\u00e4chsten Bundesregierung zu. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.760", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das kann es wirklich nicht sein."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.320", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Koalitionsvertrag besteht aus vielen Seiten; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.600", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es gibt darin aber leider keinen einzigen Abschnitt zu den Ostrenten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.760", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lediglich die Bemerkung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.480", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass f\u00fcr H\u00e4rtef\u00e4lle im Renten\u00fcberleitungsprozess ein Ausgleich durch eine Fondsl\u00f6sung geschaffen werden muss, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.960", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "findet sich darin. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.120", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Leider machen Sie keine Angaben zur H\u00f6he des Fonds und zur Definition der H\u00e4rtef\u00e4lle. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.200", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir fordern eine Aufarbeitung der F\u00e4lle, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.600", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die bei der Renten\u00fcberleitung nicht bzw. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "140.800", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht ausreichend ber\u00fccksichtigt wurden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "140.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.160", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Au\u00dferdem brauchen wir eine schnellere Angleichung der Ostrenten an die Westrenten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.000", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was f\u00fcr die FDP die Hoteliers waren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.160", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sind f\u00fcr die kleine GroKo die Verleger. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.120", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zur Sicherung der bundesweiten Versorgung mit Presseerzeugnissen soll der Arbeitgeberanteil zur Rentenversicherung bei Zeitungszustellern f\u00fcr die Dauer von f\u00fcnf Jahren von 15 auf 5\u00a0Prozent sinken. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.120", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit soll wohl die positive mediale Pr\u00e4senz der Koalitionsparteien auf Kosten der Zeitungszusteller erkauft werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.400", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ist Ihnen eigentlich bewusst, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.240", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Arbeitnehmeranteil der Zeitungszusteller, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.440", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die zumeist auf Mini-Job-Basis arbeiten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.520", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit von 3,6 auf 13,6\u00a0Prozent ansteigt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.560", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "viele Zeitungszusteller das folglich nicht tragen und sich von der Rentenversicherungspflicht befreien lassen werden? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.160", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Merken Sie eigentlich nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.040", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie mit Ihrer Politik die Altersarmut von morgen kreieren?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.880", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.760", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Genossen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.280", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "so wird das nichts mit der sozialen Gerechtigkeit und schon gar nichts mit einer zukunftsorientierten Sozialpolitik."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.360", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.560", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herzlichen Dank.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.960", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als N\u00e4chstes f\u00fcr die CDU/CSU-Fraktion der Kollege Peter Wei\u00df."
   ]
  }
 ]
}